<h2 id="3---Evaluate-Goodness-of-fit">3 - Evaluate Goodness-of-fit<a class="anchor-link" href="#3---Evaluate-Goodness-of-fit">&#182;</a></h2><p>Define the residuals:
$$
\hat{\epsilon} := x - \hat{x} = x - X\hat{a}
$$</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="Error-Decomposition">Error Decomposition<a class="anchor-link" href="#Error-Decomposition">&#182;</a></h3><p>Sample mean:
$$
\bar{x} = \frac{1}{n-p}\sum_{i=p+1}^n x_i
$$</p>
<p>Total Sum of Squares (total variability):
$$
\mathrm{TSS} := \|x-\bar{x}\|_2^2
$$</p>
<p>Residual Sum of Squares (unexplained variability):
$$
\mathrm{RSS} := \|x - X\hat{a}\|_2^2
$$</p>
<p>Explained Sum of Squares (explained variability):
$$
\mathrm{ESS} := |X\hat{a}-\bar{x}|_2^2</p>
$$
---

### $R^2$ Definition

$$<p>R^2 = \frac{\text{Explained Variability}}{\text{Total Variability}} = 1-\frac{\text{Unexplained Variability}}{\text{Explained Variability}}=1-\frac{\mathrm{RSS}}{\mathrm{TSS}}
$$</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
